snippet.title: Not Using Storyboard Leads to Getting Hired as an iOS Developer
snippet.description:
Getting hired as an iOS developer is becoming increasingly difficult as there is more and more competition out in the field.  One way to stand out is to learn how to build applications without having to rely on Storyboards. At the end of the day, companies are looking to hire people that can code and program.  Hope Caleb's story inspires and motivates people to learn the coding way of things.
